					<strong>What principles do we follow?</strong>
				</p>
				<p class="body text-secondary mb-4">
					We adhere to the principles of openness, innovation, and user-centricity.
				</p>
				<p class="body text-secondary mb-4">
					<strong>What is important to us?</strong>
